# {{name}}

This is a [Git scraping](https://simonwillison.net/series/git-scraping/) mirror of Toronto's [{{name}}]({{url}}) data set.

## Database

This project builds an SQLite database of the data, as well as a [Datasette](https://datasette.io/) image to explore the data.
Download the [latest version](https://github.com/{{repo}}/releases/latest) of database from the [releases](https://github.com/{{repo}}/releases) page.

Run the latest published image with Docker:

```
docker run -p 8000:8000 ghcr.io/{{repo}}:latest
```

Or build the database locally and run the image with Docker Compose:

```
make {{name}}.db
docker compose up
```

